[SIZE=6][COLOR=#ff66ff]✨ Core Customization Features ✨[/COLOR][/SIZE]
[/CENTER]

[CENTER][SIZE=4]
[B]Full Fishing Rod Customization[/B]: Customize all attributes of fishing rods as needed, with no quantity limits.
[B]Full Fish Customization[/B]: Adjust all parameters of fish according to your preferences, with no quantity limits.
[B]Full Bait Customization[/B]: Design personalized baits freely, with no quantity limits.
[B]Full Competition Customization[/B]: Create various fishing competitions independently, with no quantity limits.
[B]Language Customization[/B]: Select and set the language version you require (zh_CN / en_US).
[B]Full Fishing Hook Customization[/B]: Modify the attributes of fishing hooks, with no quantity limits.
[B]Intelligent Pricing Function[/B]: Support automatic pricing (for selling) based on the size and quality of fish.
[B]Advanced Statistics[/B]: Track detailed fishing statistics and player records via bStats.
[B]Visual Effects[/B]: Customizable particle effects and animations for enhanced fishing experience.
[B]Folia & Spigot Dual Support[/B]: Dedicated kkfish-folia.jar build for Folia/Foila servers.
[B]Performance Optimized[/B]: Efficient code structure with minimal server impact.
[B]Regular Updates[/B]: Continuous feature expansions and improvements.
[/SIZE][/CENTER]

